    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Made from an alloy of steel and brass to be as flexible as possible, with a string fashioned from steel and nickel, this shortbow requires the strength of a giant to be fully drawn. The user must be careful, as applying more strength than necessary can permanently bend the bow, rendering it unusable, they must be powerful but graceful.</p><section class=\"secret\" id=\"secret-CXps2WXM9KpbfY22\"><p><strong>Note for DMs</strong></p><p>This item possesses no fixed stats, this is by design. The GM/DM is advised to modify the stats to best fit their world, setting and story. Due to those factors, all stats can vary wildly.</p></section>",
